title: Greenify ROOT v2.2 Build 3 + Donation Package v2.3 - the.HH
description:
[center][code]Release info:
1) Install Xposed installer
2) Install Greenify donation 2.3 key
3) Install Greenify
4) Open Xposed installer, select greenify inside modules tab, open framework tab then press install/update & reboot
5) Done!


[/code]
[b]This version supports Android Runtime (ART) In KitKat![/b]


[i]Enjoy![/i]
